Subject: [PATCH] platform/x86/intel/pmc: Add Lunar Lake support to Intel PMC SSRAM Telemetry
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2d5a84c3ecc075d87bcb16c1cc80277b5837c153
